content:
In all honesty, I see this as a completely flawless anime, even after months idle without having seen it. Usually anime that I considered amazing, my opinions would change after a while. Everything about this anime was outstanding, especially the soundtrack. Any time I hear some of the songs play, it makes me want to cry. 
Even though it seems I have only good things to say, I wouldn't recommend this for a lot of people. It contains A LOT of sexual content, and *Spoils* contains incest. A lot of people are really bothered by this subject, and it ruins the entire experience for them,but if you're like me, and you aren't really phased by much, I really do recommend this anime. It touched my heart more times than you can imagine, and I still hold it dear to me. \n\n
If only they would make a NA DVD release ;-;
